@startuml UC_22_Report_Violation
title UC-22: Report Violation

|User|
start
:(1) Open the report form from a post, comment, or community;
:(2) Enter the reason and details;
:(3) Submit the report;

|System|
:(4) Validate authentication and report data;
:(5) Create the report record;
:(6) Store it as pending review;
:(7) Return confirmation;

stop
@enduml
